    "ShortDescription": {
      "Namespace": "",
      "Key": "DBFBE8B6465FFA5A5CDA0E80467BBD54",
      "SourceString": "<text color=\"FFFFFFFF\" fontface=\"black\" size=\"20\" Case=\"AllCaps\">Call the lightning and wield the powers of Thor with the Gods of Thunder Pack. This offer will no longer be available as of August 21st '24 00:00 UTC, and may return in the future.</>\r\n\r\n<text color=\"00E2FFFF\" fontface=\"black\" size=\"16\" Case=\"AllCaps\">The Reformed Mjolnir Pickaxe and Mjolnir's Flight Glider can only be used by the Thor Odinson, Mighty Thor, Thor, and Captain America Outfits. Reformed Mjolnir includes a built-in emote. The Stormbreaker Pickaxe and Stormbreaker's Flight Glider are usable by all Outfits, so long as they are mighty and brave...</>\r\n\r\nThis pack contains:",
      "LocalizedString": "<text color=\"FFFFFFFF\" fontface=\"black\" size=\"20\" Case=\"AllCaps\">Call the lightning and wield the powers of Thor with the Gods of Thunder Pack. This offer will no longer be available as of August 21st '24 00:00 UTC, and may return in the future.</>\r\n\r\n<text color=\"00E2FFFF\" fontface=\"black\" size=\"16\" Case=\"AllCaps\">The Reformed Mjolnir Pickaxe and Mjolnir's Flight Glider can only be used by the Thor Odinson, Mighty Thor, Thor, and Captain America Outfits. Reformed Mjolnir includes a built-in emote. The Stormbreaker Pickaxe and Stormbreaker's Flight Glider are usable by all Outfits, so long as they are mighty and brave...</>\r\n\r\nThis pack contains:"
    },
